tafsir[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,127,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen alaa wa…ói, si wanaa fennugol mo. Awa …óum wonay sabu …ìe tawnoyteebe e lepte …óen."
  37,128,"Si wanaa …ìen yim…ìe makko gom…óinnoo…ìe la…ì…ìini dewe mun …ìen, …ìen …óon da…óoyay tawnoyeede e lepte …óen."
  37,129,"Men accani mo mantoore e jantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitii…ìe …ìen."
  37,130,"Alla hiwrike mantii Ilyaasna'en."
  37,131,"Ko wano Men yo…ìitiri non Ilyaasa'en, woni ko Men yo…ìitirta jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen."
  37,132,"Kanko Ilyaasa, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe goongini gom…óingol Joomi mun."
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ìe Alla …ìen nuliranoo…ìe e yim…ìe mun, wewlingol e jertingol."
