  37,136,"Refti Men halki fennunoo…ìe mo, heddii …ìe …ìen."
  37,137,"Onon yim…ìe Makkah …ìen non, hi…óon rewa e galleeji ma…ì…ìe, tuma setorton Saami, e dawol mon."
  37,138,"Hi…óon rewa e hoore-ma…ì…ìe kadi, ka jemma. E on haqqiltaa, waajitoron ko he…ìi …ìe kon, …ìaawo …ìe fennude …ìe yedda …ìe faggitoo bonunnda mo adaaka e mun?"
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ìe Alla …ìen nuliranoo…ìe e yim…ìe mun, wewlingol e jertingol."
  37,140,"Janto nde o dogunoo yim…ìe makko …ìen, ko aldaa e du≈ãayee Joomi makko. O wa…ó…óoyii laana hebbiniraaka yim…ìe e dolle."
  37,141,"Laana kan e…ì…ìi yoolagol, hakkee ko ka heewi. ∆Åe urbinii nder ton, ndaarugol ko hom…ìe gasetee bugedee ka maayo, fii …óuytugol teddeendi makka ndin; Yuunusa jeyaa e …ìen foolaa…ìe ka urba, …ìe bugii mo ka maayo."
  37,142,"Nde …ìe buginoo mo ka maayo, linngii ngii mo…ói mo, fewndo ka o felnii; tawde o yehii ka maayo, o du≈ãinaaki e Joomi makko."
  37,143,"Si wanaano tawde Yuunusa ko jeyanoo…óo e jantotoo…ìe Alla ko …óuu…ói, si wanaano subbunhinagol makko ngol ka nder reedu lingii ngii"
